    • Method Detail

      • createNode

        public static <D1 extends LinkedRBKey<D1>> LinkedRBNode<D1> createNode​(D1 data)
        Creates a new LinkedRBNode. Automatically links the key to the node.
        This factory design pattern is used to prevent leaking of this instance during initialisation.
        Type Parameters:
        D1 - The type of the node to be initialised.
        Parameters:
        data - The data of the new node.
        Returns:
        A freshly initialised node.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the given data already belongs to another linked node.
